\f2\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 \'a0Inversion targets: MEaSUREs observed surface velocity field (Mouginot 2019,\
with low-velocity gap-filling from MeasuresChange).\
Cost functions: velocity misfit + Tikhonov regularization on B and C.\
SMB correction tuning \
after the historical run (1995\'962020), modelled mass change per region is compared\
against GRACE/GRACE-FO observations (Otosaka et al. 2023) by comparing mass trends. \
 A per-region scale\
factor p_vert is applied to the RACMO climatology component to minimize the\
trend mismatch (WAIS +5.5 %, EAIS +3.6 %, Peninsula \uc0\u8722 2.8 %, capped at \'b125 %).\
BMB is tuned after the tuning protocol.\
