\f2\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 7. What parameterization is used to migrate the grounding line? How are partially floating cells treated?\'a0\
Grounding line migration: SubelementMigration (ISSM).\
Partially floating cells: SubelementFriction1 for basal friction,\
SubelementMelt1 for basal melt at partially floating elements.\
The floating criterion uses the standard hydrostatic flotation conditi
\f1\fs24 \
